          - mLabel: Simple Reflection
            mType: Define
            mName: ENABLE_SIMPLE_REFLECTION
            mWidget: group_start
            mHint: |-
              Define: ENABLE_SIMPLE_REFLECTION
              
              Replaces the default PBR environment mapping with a simple lookup from a regular texture (no hdr, no roughness, no fresnel, etc.). 
              It can even be used with unlit materials. The reflection lookup technically assumes a spherical environment map, which is a circular 
              shaped texture as obtained by photographing a mirror ball. However, as a shortcut, it is sometimes used with simple, flat photos, and 
              manually bent mesh normals. Note: this spherical mapping is technically different from the 'angular' envmap format that looks similar.
            mMin: ~
            mMax: ~
            mStep: ~
            mDefaultVal: ~
            mValues:
              []
